    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to a style and school of influential Chinese landscape painting. Yuan dynasty painters such as Huang Gongwang, Wu Zhen, and Zhao Mengfu were greatly influenced by the Dong-Ju style.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000008541/Miyagawa, Chinese Painting (1983)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Se refiere a un estilo y a una escuela de la pintura china influyente en el paisaje. El estilo de Dong-Ju influenciaron a los pintores de la dinastía de Yuan tales como Huang Gongwang, Wu Zhen, y Zhao Mengfu.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar een invloedrijke stijl en school van Chinese landschapsschilderkunst. Schilders uit de Yuan-dynastie, zoals Huang Gongwang, Wu Zhen en Zhao Mengfu, waren sterk beïnvloed door de Dong-Ju-stijl.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>深具影響力的一個中國山水畫風及畫派。黃公望、吳鎮、趙孟頫等元代畫家均深受董源（西元１０世紀末）和巨然（西元960-980）風格影響。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
